prodNameC: 連宏德國麻疹檢驗試劑
ingredientsDesc:
Latex reagent (1 x 1.6 ml): Suspension of polystyrene latex particles coated with rubella virus antigen in a buffer. Contains < 0.1% sodium azide.
Positive control (1 x 1.0 ml): Diluted positive human serum. Contains < 0.1% sodium azide.
Negative control (1 x 1.0 ml): Diluted normal human serum. Contains < 0.1% sodium azide.
Dilution buffer (1 x 50 ml): Phosphate buffered saline, containing bovine serum albumin. Contains < 0.1% sodium azide.
Disposable slides: 13 units (x8)
